                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "8b30b9256178684bb3d817f553b1b33c",
                "text": "A general feat with the skill trait improves your skills and their actions or gives you new actions for a skill. A feat with this trait can be selected when a class grants a skill feat or general feat. Archetype feats with the skill trait can be selected in place of a skill feat if you have that archetype\u2019s dedication feat."
